componentLogic

public java.util.ArrayList<AP2DXMessage> componentLogic(Message message)
Does the logic for the Reflex module. That is:
- check if there is something in front of the vehicle and stop the motor.
- forward messages from the Planner to the motor if there is nothing.

doOverride

public void doOverride()
Description copied from class: AP2DXBase
If needed, extra logic for the constructor of the concrete class can be added here. This is nessecary because the component constructor calls super() but will never return. It waits for the BaseLogic to return.
